title: Alone in the Dark 2 playthrough
description: Holy shit. I thought Alone in the Dark was a horror franchise, but this is a pirate game. It's just straight up pirate adventure. Also it's confusing as fuck, difficult as hell, and annoying as shit. Still enjoyed it though. Had to use a walkthrough though otherwise it would've taken forever. Gonna play the rest of em, hope they're better...
